Retrieve a list of payment methods on file for a user. When in Sandbox, `type` will be `credit` and `brand` will be `visa`.

### HTTP Request

`POST <%= config.host %>/payment/list`

### Post Parameters

Param | Description
----- | -----------
`clientId` | Unbill client ID.

### Returns

A dictionary with a `data` property that contains an array of payment method objects.